text: Tanybria costata is a species of leaf beetle of Cameroon and the Democratic Republic of the Congo, observed by Martin Jacoby in 1898. ==References== Category:Eumolpinae Category:Beetles of Africa Category:Insects of Cameroon Category:Beetles of the Democratic Republic of the Congo Category:Taxa named by Martin Jacoby Category:Beetles described in 1898
title: Tanybria costata
